sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant DeviceA as Device A (OS Version 1)
    participant DeviceB as Device B (OS Version 2)
    participant Server as Server

    User->>DeviceA: Initiate connection
    DeviceA->>Server: Request compatibility info
    Server-->>DeviceA: Provide compatibility data
    DeviceA->>DeviceB: Send connection request
    DeviceB-->>DeviceA: Acknowledge connection
    DeviceA->>User: Connection established
    DeviceB->>User: Connection established